# StudySync Pro — Full Website Rebuild

## Overview
Complete professional redesign of StudySync into a multi-section, responsive web app with premium features, separated into HTML + CSS + JS files.

## Proposed Changes

### File Structure
```
entrepreneurship/StudySync/
├── index.html       — Main shell + all sections
├── style.css        — Full design system + animations
└── app.js           — All JavaScript logic
```

### Sections & Features

#### 1. Navigation (Sticky, Glassmorphism)
- Logo + hamburger menu for mobile
- Smooth scroll/section reveal with hover glow effects
- Active section indicator

#### 2. Home Hero
- Animated gradient background
- CTA buttons → Features / Login

#### 3. Features Grid
- Cards with hover lift + glow
- 6 features: Timer, Rooms, Leaderboard, Chat, Premium, Ads

#### 4. Pomodoro Timer
- Custom minutes/seconds input
- Progress circle animation
- Session counter + streak tracking
- Scores feed to leaderboard

#### 5. Study Room
- Room list with member avatars
- Join/Leave + status badge
- Background ambient sound toggle

#### 6. Rank Leaderboard
- Top 10 students sorted by total study minutes
- Gold/Silver/Bronze medals for top 3
- Animated rank bars

#### 7. Group Chat
- Bubble-style messages
- Timestamp + avatar initials
- Enter key send

#### 8. Profile & Verification
- Modal: create profile (name, avatar color, goal)
- Gold ✓ badge for users with 10+ hours studied
- Stats: sessions, total time, streak

#### 9. Premium Section
- Pricing cards (Free / Pro / Team)
- Feature comparison list
- Shimmer CTA button

#### 10. Advertisement Section
- Rotating student-relevant banners (internships, courses, tools)
- Dismissible ad cards

#### 11. Footer
- Links + social icons + copyright

## Design System
- **Font**: Outfit (Google Fonts)
- **Colors**: Deep navy `#050d1a`, card dark `#0f1f35`, accent cyan `#22d3ee`, premium gold `#f59e0b`
- **Effects**: Glassmorphism cards, gradient text, micro-animations, smooth transitions (0.4s ease)
- **Responsive**: Mobile-first breakpoints at 768px and 480px
